      "text": "優、入るわね。雑誌撮影の見本誌が届いたから……\nあ、ごめんなさい。漫画を描いていたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ I'll go in. The sample magazine photoshoot has arrived…\nOh‚ sorry. You were drawing a manga",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1000022251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
