      "text": "気にせんといて。今から始めるとこやったから\n全然集中してへんかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry. I'm just getting started\nI wasn't concentrating at all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9333355585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
