      "text": "なら良かった。それにしても、優は本当に絵が上手ね\n今度、グッズのデザインをしてみたら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's good. By the way‚ Yu is really good at drawing\nThis time‚ how about trying designing goods?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4666695276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7333361942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
