      "text": "も～、そんなに褒めんといてよ\nけど瑠依ちゃんやすみれちゃんを描くんは楽しそうやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on~‚ don't praise me so much\nBut‚ it looks like it would be fun to draw Rui-chan and Sumire-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7333361942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7000028609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、今から試しに描いてみない？\n似顔絵、どんな感じになるのか気になるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ why don't you try drawing it now?\nI wonder what caricature will look like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7000028609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
